### Dashboard API Tests

# Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8088/api/v1
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Dashboard Summary (Authenticated User)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2. Get Dashboard Summary by User ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. Get User Profile (to get user info)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Get Badge Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/badge/summary/1?limit=6
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Get All Badges
GET {{baseUrl}}/badge/all/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6. Get Badge Progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/badge/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 7. Get Earned Badges
GET {{baseUrl}}/badge/earned
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 8. Get Recent Badges
GET {{baseUrl}}/badge/recent/1?limit=6
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 9. Get Vocabulary Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/vocab/stats/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 10. Get Grammar Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/grammar/stats/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 11. Force Check Badges (Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/badge/check
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
